item.title: Aspose.Cells for SharePoint - Use and Benefits
item.description: SharePoint sites are meant for collaboration, communication and content storage in order to fulfill particular business needs. Aspose.Cells for SharePoint has been introduced to perform certain operations on Microsoft Excel documents available in SharePoint document libraries. This article covers the following: A brief note about SharePoint document libraries. The benefits Aspose.Cells for SharePoint. How to convert Microsoft Excel documents into other formats. A Brief Note on SharePoint Document Libraries
